Perceptor/Blacknightmare::


Blacknightmare walked inside the Blackfortress and she reported to 
Perceptor. They were in Perceptors's office, Perceptor was 
downloading some information thanks a special program.  

"What're our duties?" asked the femme

"Find out  how many new bots are in this place" Replied the second in 
rank "registed them, and give them a status here"

"Pretty easy..." replied the femme

"We have to start " replied Perceptor.

Blacknightmare nodded and left the office and walked towards 
Commounication Room.

Perceptor left the office and went to Conference room.
